Name: 2025 U.S. Open Golf Championship
Title: Final Round
Desc: The 125th U.S. Open comes to an end with the final round from Oakmont Country Club in Pennsylvania.
LongDescription: The 125th U.S. Open comes to an end with the final round from Oakmont Country Club. In 1973, Johnny Miller shot the first 63 in major championship history to erase a six-stroke, 54-hole deficit and claim his only U.S. Open title at Oakmont.
